      <ul>
        <li><strong>CTOS Score:</strong> Below 650 = auto reject</li>
        <li><strong>Payment History:</strong> Late payments flagged</li>
        <li><strong>Defaults:</strong> Previous loans unpaid</li>
        <li><strong>CCRIS:</strong> Too many enquiries</li>
        <li><strong>Policy:</strong> Strict computer approval</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Approve Bad Credit</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Human Review:</strong> Real person looks at your case</li>
        <li><strong>Story Matters:</strong> We listen to explanation</li>
        <li><strong>Business Focus:</strong> Can you repay? That's important</li>
        <li><strong>Asset Value:</strong> Crane is good security</li>
        <li><strong>Future Potential:</strong> Not just past problems</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Bank vs. Ing Heng Credit</h2>

      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <thead>
          <tr style="background: #D4A574; color: #2D1810;">
            <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #B8945A;">Factor</th>
            <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #B8945A;">Bank</th>
            <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #B8945A;">Ing Heng Credit</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>Bad Credit</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Rejected</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong style="color: #D4A574;">Considered</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background: #F9FAFB;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>CTOS Score</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Must be high</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong style="color: #D4A574;">Not critical</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>Down Payment</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">20-30%</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong style="color: #D4A574;">0%</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background: #F9FAFB;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>Approval</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Computer says no</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong style="color: #D4A574;">Human decides</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>Time</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">2-4 weeks</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong style="color: #D4A574;">fasts</strong></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Common Bad Credit Reasons</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Business Loss:</strong> Pandemic affected income</li>
        <li><strong>Client Default:</strong> Customers didn't pay you</li>
        <li><strong>Medical:</strong> Health problems caused debt</li>
        <li><strong>Divorce:</strong> Family issues impacted finances</li>
        <li><strong>Previous Business:</strong> Failed venture</li>
        <li><strong>Guarantor:</strong> Helped someone who defaulted</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>We Understand Real Life</h2>

      <p>Banks see numbers. We see people. We know:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>COVID-19 hurt many businesses</li>
        <li>Construction slows down sometimes</li>
        <li> Clients delay payments</li>
        <li>Life happens unexpectedly</li>
        <li>Good people have bad luck</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What We Need for Approval</h2>

      <h3>1. Your Story</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Explain what happened</li>
        <li>Be honest about problems</li>
        <li>Show how you're fixing it</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>2. Current Business</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Active contracts or projects</li>
        <li>Income statements</li>
        <li>Bank statements (6 months)</li>
        <li>Business registration</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>3. Crane Details</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Which crane you need</li>
        <li>How it will generate income</li>
