      <h2>Rebuild Your Credit</h2>

      <p>Getting crane financing helps rebuild credit:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>On-Time Payments:</strong> We report good payment history</li>
        <li><strong>Asset Ownership:</strong> Builds your net worth</li>
        <li><strong>Business Growth:</strong> Better income improves score</li>
        <li><strong>Future Access:</strong> Easier financing next time</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Success Story</h2>

      <p>"Had bad credit from failed business 2020. CTOS score 520. Bank rejected everything. Needed 50-ton mobile crane for new contracts. Bank said NO. Found Ing Heng online. Applied and explained my situation. Past business failed due to partner cheating. New business is good with contracts. Ing Heng approved in fasts. 0% down payment. 100% full loan. Got crane. Completed projects. Paid on time every month. CTOS score now 680. Business grown from 1 crane to 3. Ing Heng gave me second chance when nobody would."</p>

